      <div class="msgContentFrame">I feel your pain with regards to the success rates on crafting, and it's something SE has said they're working on.  I always found it frustrating to start a synthesis on the usually white orb but not be offered any of my equipped abilities and fail the first action for 20+ durability lost.  Even worse when the orb stays white, you're not offered any of your abilities for your second action either, and you get another failed action for another 20+ durability lost. <br /> <br />I'm looking forward to seeing what SE has in mind to remedy the issue.</div>
